<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">}</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>你可以用 Lambda 来实现这个接口：</p>
